title: Page & Plant - No Quarter: Unledded (assembled by }{eywood)
description:
Page & Plant
No Quarter: Unledded
assembled by }{eywood

Although this follows the running order of the DVD it is made up from the DVD audio and the CD versions.  The mixes on the CD were better than the ones on the video, particularly the song No Quarter, which is essentially mono on the video version but very stereo on the CD.  I therefore took the best versions of each for listening and made up this full version
